WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:24.580 --> 00:00:26.500
 100g flour, 3 etl sugar 

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:28.740
 1 etl cornflour, a pinch of salt 

00:00:28.740 --> 00:00:29.860
 1 egg, 100 ml milk and 1 etl oil 

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:37.640
 Sieve all the ingredients in a bowl. 

00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:55.100
 Mix well with a whisk. 

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:01.240
 beat one egg in another bowl 

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:05.700
 add milk and mix well 

00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.500
 add the dry ingredients 

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:12.360
 1/3 at a time 

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:30.980
 add oil 

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:31.540
 mix well 

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.600
 cover with cling film and let rest for 5 minutes 

